title: A keynote: Beachbody Coach Summit 2016
description: What an event. Something like 20,000+ Beachbody coaches all fired up to build their own businesses. I love the fitness industry but just like in fitness, your business is never going to grow unless you put the work in day-in and day-out. Such an honor and pleasure to speak in front of so many hustlers, BUT, that doesn't mean they didn't need some extra fire to get them going. Believe me, I BROUGHT IT. This one needs a listen.
